                  <msItemStruct>
                     <note type="general">5 lines written along the fibers; the back is blank; the letter was folded six times</note>
                     <note type="general">Written in the small neat hand of Zenon (or his favorite clerk), cf. P.Col.III 58 and 59 and IV 72 and 75, and p. 40</note>
                     <note type="general">There is a large check mark on the bottom left part: maybe the letter was returned after completion of the commissions</note>
